{{ $('Parameter Parser').first().json.output?.referenceUsageInstruction ? 'IMPORTANT: When using the reference image, ' + $('Parameter Parser').first().json.output.referenceUsageInstruction : 'Use reference image for overall style matching.' }}

## Format:
{{ $('Parameter Parser').first().json.output?.aspectRatio === '9:16' ? 'Portrait/vertical format' : $('Parameter Parser').first().json.output?.aspectRatio === '1:1' ? 'Square format' : 'Widescreen/landscape format (16:9)' }}

